#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Asilomasutta → asi-sūkariko (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Asilomasutta"
msgstr "5. Sword Hairs"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.257"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn19.5:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ asilomaṃ purisaṃ "
"vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw "
"a man whose body hairs were swords flying through the air."

msgctxt "sn19.5:1.2"
msgid "Tassa te asī uppatitvā uppatitvā tasseva kāye nipatanti."
msgstr "And those swords kept rising up and falling on his body"

msgctxt "sn19.5:1.3"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe …"
msgstr "as he screamed in pain. …” …"

msgctxt "sn19.5:1.4"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe sūkariko ahosi … pe …."
msgstr "“That being used to be a pig butcher right here in Rājagaha. …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.5:1.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
